pageTitle: Itinerary for Sunday, March 19, 2017 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Itinerary for the Prime Minister, Justin Trudeau, for Sunday, March 19, 2017:

Montréal, Quebec

12:00 p.m. The Prime Minister will participate in the St. Patrick’s Parade in Montréal.

Note for media:

  • Open coverage
